62
00:05:19,840 --> 00:05:21,600
He is waiting for you
in the charging room upstairs.

63
00:05:22,520 --> 00:05:23,320
You two may talk.

64
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:24,640
I'll get going.

65
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:33,800
Charging room?

66
00:06:57,320 --> 00:06:58,760
