69
00:07:21,440 --> 00:07:23,000
This is a mechanical heart.

70
00:07:23,920 --> 00:07:26,120
I need to recharge it to stay alive.

71
00:07:31,640 --> 00:07:32,680
So...

72
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,720
